<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Philadelphia</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>ὑπόμνημα Ζήνωνι παρὰ Ἀγάθωνος. περὶ ὧν σοι 

    <lb n="2"/>ἐμπεφάνικα, ἵνα κ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">α</unclear>ὶ κο<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">μ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ι</supplied>δήν τινα ποιήσηι, πρὸ <app type="editorial"><lem>τοῦ</lem><rdg>πι<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">σ</unclear>τοῦ</rdg></app> 

    <lb n="3"/>βασιλικὰ γενέσθαι· ὀφείλει γὰρ εἰς τὸ βασιλικὸν πολλά· 

    <lb n="4a"/>καὶ διδάξω ὅθεν τὴν κομιδὴν <choice><corr>ποιήσει</corr><sic>ποησει</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="4"/>καὶ περὶ ὧν σοι δύναμαι χρήσιμος γενέσθαι, ὥστε σε 

    <lb n="5"/>προσωφελεῖν <add place="supralinear">ἐκ τῆς γῆς</add> <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">εἰς τὸ βασιλικὸν</del> οὐκ ὀλίγον. εἰσὶν δὲ <expan><ex cert="high">ἄρουραι</ex></expan> <num value="265">σξε</num> 

    <lb n="6"/>ἃς <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">γε</supplied>ωργεῖ Πετοβάστις. ἀξιῶ οὖν παραδοθῆναί 

    <lb n="7"/>μοι ταύτας. ἐγὼ δέ σοι, ὅσην ἂν σιτοφορήσω ἀνα-

    <lb n="8"/>πληρώσω ἀκίνδυνον <expan>πυρ<ex cert="high">ῶν</ex></expan> <expan><ex cert="high">ἀρτάβας</ex></expan> <num value="10">ι</num>· εἰ δὲ μή, <num value="10">ι</num> <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> τὴν <expan><ex cert="high">ἄρουραν</ex></expan>. 

    <lb n="9"/>σὺ δὲ δύνηι ἐκ <num value="4">δ</num> <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμῶν</ex></expan> διαλύειν τὰ ἐκφόρια, ὥστε μηθὲν 

    <lb n="10"/>βλάπτεσθαί σε, ἀλλ᾽ ὠφελεῖσθαι <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="6">ϛ</num>. ἀναπαύσεις δὲ 

    <lb n="11"/>κατ᾽ ἐνιαυτὸν <expan><ex cert="high">ἄρουρας</ex></expan> <num value="100">ρ</num>, ἐγὼ δὲ ἀναπληρώσω τὴν <expan><ex cert="high">ἄρουραν</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="12"/>χόρτου <expan>δέ<ex cert="high">σμας</ex></expan> <choice><corr><expan><ex cert="high">δι</ex></expan>μν</corr><sic><app type="editorial"><lem>βμν</lem><rdg>β<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ι</unclear>ν</rdg></app></sic></choice><expan><ex cert="high">αίους</ex></expan> <num value="1500">Αφ</num>. καὶ <choice><corr>ἐὰν</corr><sic>εαμ</sic></choice> μὲν βούληι ἐκφόρια 

    <lb n="13"/>διαλύειν· εἰ δὲ μή, τιμῆς τὴν <expan><ex cert="high">ἄρουραν</ex></expan> <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="3">γ</num>. ὅσα δ᾽ ἂν 

    <lb n="14"/>χλωρὰ τὰ κτήνη ἐξανηλώσηι σου ἀνυπόλογόν σοι 

    <lb n="15"/>οἴσω, <add place="supralinear">σοῦ παρέχοντος τὸ σπέρμα</add> ὥστε καὶ τὰ κτήνη σου ἔχειν χορτάσματα 

    <lb n="16"/>δωρεάν. καὶ διδάξω σε ὅτι λύει. ὀψώνιον δέ μοι τά-

    <lb n="17"/>ξεις <choice><corr>σὺν</corr><sic>συμ</sic></choice> παντὶ κατὰ μῆνα <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="10">ι</num>. οὐ γὰρ προς 

    <lb n="18"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>επι<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> </ab></div><div n="meta.2083" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.2083" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="-275" notAfter="-226">Mitte III v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.2083" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Gehört zum Zenon - Archiv.</p></div><div n="meta.2083" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head></div><div n="meta.2083" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">PSI</title><biblScope type="volume">4</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">400</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">2083</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0238</series>; <biblScope type="volume">4</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">400</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0238;4;400" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.2083" type="bibliography" subtype="corrections" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">X</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">239</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">XI</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">244</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.2083" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><bibl type="illustration" default